creator: Optherium
descriptionHtml:
Get your own personal European Euro currency IBAN account and Omniwire Prepaid Mastercard® in less than 5 minutes with Omniwire Money. Send and receive money globally with SWIFT and SEPA payments.

Virtual & Physical Prepaid Debit Card
Spend money 24/7 at millions of locations and websites in 210 countries and territories across the globe with Omniwire Prepaid Mastercard®.

Frictionless online registration
Pass our user-friendly registration online within less than 5 minutes and get instant access to your account and start using your account straight away.

Top up your balance with ease
Replenish your balance instantly with SWIFT, SEPA direct, Visa, Mastercard, and alternative payment methods.

Protect money with your biometry
Keep your account secure from hackers with the passwordless biometric verification feature. Login and confirm operations with your face scan or fingerprint signature.

Stay in control of your money
Analyze and manage spendings, set up limits, block cards remotely, and much more through a user-friendly interface and numerous money management tools.

Feature-reach solution
Enjoy dozens of useful money management tools within a user-friendly interface enhanced with a reach functionality:
- International Money Transfers
- Send, receive, and request payments worldwide
- Recurring Payments
- Pay utility bills & repeating payments automatically
- Request money from any person globally via the link
- Easily split and pay the bill with friends & family
- Set up Favorite Payments
- Track spending history
- And much more

Money Security
Omniwire Money utilizes biometric authentication security and settles funds in the Central Bank of Ireland to make sure your money is safe.

Friendly Support
Our customer support managers are always friendly and ready to answer all of your questions 24/7

Digital-only Platform
Omniwire Money is a fully digital platform that allows access to financial services without the need of visiting a brick and mortar bank branch.

How to start
1. Install the application
Download the Omniwire Money application to your device.
2. Register
Upload a scanned file or photo of your ID document, issued in the EEA, and make a selfie photo.
3. Choose Plan
You can choose a plan and a rate which would be comfortable for you.
4. Use services anytime
Enjoy the benefits of using Omniwire Prepaid Mastercard® and European IBAN globally 24/7.

Omniwire Prepaid Mastercard® Issuer Statement
The Omniwire Prepaid Mastercard® is issued by PFS Card Services (Ireland) Limited pursuant to a license from Mastercard® International Incorporated. PFS Card Services (Ireland) Limited, trading as PCSIL, is regulated by the Central Bank of Ireland.

Spend money 24/7 at millions of locations and websites in 210 countries and territories across the globe with Omniwire Prepaid Mastercard®.

Frictionless online registration
Pass our user-friendly registration online within less than 5 minutes and get instant access to your account and start using your account straight away.

Top up your balance with ease
Replenish your balance instantly with SWIFT, SEPA direct, Visa, Mastercard, and alternative payment methods.

Protect money with your biometry
Keep your account secure from hackers with the passwordless biometric verification feature. Login and confirm operations with your face scan or fingerprint signature.

Stay in control of your money
Analyze and manage spendings, set up limits, block cards remotely, and much more through a user-friendly interface and numerous money management tools.

Feature-reach solution
Enjoy dozens of useful money management tools within a user-friendly interface enhanced with a reach functionality:
- International Money Transfers
- Send, receive, and request payments worldwide
- Recurring Payments
- Pay utility bills & repeating payments automatically
- Request money from any person globally via the link
- Easily split and pay the bill with friends & family
- Set up Favorite Payments
- Track spending history
- And much more

Money Security
Omniwire Money utilizes biometric authentication security and settles funds in the Central Bank of Ireland to make sure your money is safe.

Friendly Support
Our customer support managers are always friendly and ready to answer all of your questions 24/7

Digital-only Platform
Omniwire Money is a fully digital platform that allows access to financial services without the need of visiting a brick and mortar bank branch.

How to start
1. Install the application
Download the Omniwire Money application to your device.
2. Register
Upload a scanned file or photo of your ID document, issued in the EEA, and make a selfie photo.
3. Choose Plan
You can choose a plan and a rate which would be comfortable for you.
4. Use services anytime
Enjoy the benefits of using Omniwire Prepaid Mastercard® and European IBAN globally 24/7.

Omniwire Prepaid Mastercard® Issuer Statement
The Omniwire Prepaid Mastercard® is issued by PFS Card Services (Ireland) Limited pursuant to a license from Mastercard® International Incorporated. PFS Card Services (Ireland) Limited, trading as PCSIL, is regulated by the Central Bank of Ireland.
